_part\": \"safari\",\n          \"related_contact\": \"Emmanuel\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"a3d89255-b5b8-401b-8187-535e4c23fea5\",\n          \"title\": \"Maasai bracelet purchase at crater rim\",\n          \"body\": \"A Maasai lady at the Ngorongoro crater rim sold two beaded bracelets for Athina Mari. Paid approximately TZS 35,000 (~$20-25 USD).\",\n          \"category\": \"voice_memo\",\n          \"trip_part\": \"safari\",\n          \"related_contact\": \"\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"241fb553-a6c4-4941-bf29-900deeecdca1\",\n          \"title\": \"Extra ranger tip at Ngorongoro gate\",\n          \"body\": \"Emmanuel warned of an extra ranger tip of ~TZS 5,000 cash at the gate, separate from park fees. Vasileios wants to confirm this with Richard before the safari balance payment.\",\n          \"category\": \"voice_memo\",\n          \"trip_part\": \"safari\",\n          \"related_contact\": \"Richard (Suricata Safaris)\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"603a15be-f103-465c-afe6-d7d0178b93a8\",\n          \"title\": \"Crater day - best day of my life\",\n          \"body\": \"The Ngorongoro Crater day was described as \\\"one of the best days of my life.\\\"\",\n          \"category\": \"voice_memo\",\n          \"trip_part\": \"safari\",\n          \"related_contact\": \"\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"7e0f1146-face-4474-a54c-c513b0976f44\",\n          \"title\": \"Stone Town courtyard photo note\",\n          \"body\": \"A bright courtyard with white stucco walls, arched windows, and ornate dark balconies under a clear blue sky.\",\n          \"category\": \"photo_note\",\n          \"trip_part\": \"zanzibar\",\n          \"related_contact\": \"\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"1d816bf3-006e-429a-8252-328ec7edf87e\",\n          \"title\": \"Safari balance payment - confirm with Richard\",\n          \"body\": \"Balance $960 due on arrival in Arusha. Cash preferred (USD, post-2009 not