.tz; visa-on-arrival no longer available as of January 2025. Zanzibar also requires separate mandatory travel insurance from ZIC.\",\n          \"category\": \"key_learning\",\n          \"trip_part\": \"general\",\n          \"related_contact\": \"\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"570fef74-cab4-4ef0-b66d-ee0ab007e29a\",\n          \"title\": \"Egypt e-visa multiple-entry\",\n          \"body\": \"Egypt e-visa is multiple-entry ($65); both travelers apply separately. Egyptian e-visa requires a mandatory printed copy.\",\n          \"category\": \"key_learning\",\n          \"trip_part\": \"cairo\",\n          \"related_contact\": \"\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"e98eab5b-f02f-42b8-b634-d510420cc4bc\",\n          \"title\": \"Precision Air luggage restrictions\",\n          \"body\": \"Precision Air flights (TC144/TC145) have luggage restrictions favoring soft bags.\",\n          \"category\": \"tip\",\n          \"trip_part\": \"general\",\n          \"related_contact\": \"\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"09986e1c-a857-4c2c-a81b-fca7fc2fc8f5\",\n          \"title\": \"August is peak safari season\",\n          \"body\": \"August is peak safari season — ideal for wildlife, including the Great Wildebeest Migration corridor.\",\n          \"category\": \"observation\",\n          \"trip_part\": \"safari\",\n          \"related_contact\": \"\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"07babe3d-308a-42b0-a976-442cb253909a\",\n          \"title\": \"Zanzibar driving permit required\",\n          \"body\": \"Vasilis holds an International Driving Permit (IDP). A local Zanzibar Driving Permit is also required (~$15, valid up to 3 months). Most rental companies arrange this with a license photo provided 24+ hours before arrival. Police checkpoints are frequent; carry both IDP and local permit (screenshot acceptable).\",\n          \"category\": \"tip\",\n          \"trip_part\": \"zanzibar\",\n          \"related_contact\": \"\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"3ec610e2-92fe-4c0c-9888-28cce236ae74\",\n          \"title\": \"Cairo Stopover 1 sightseeing\",\n          \"body\": \"Grand Egyptian Museum and Pyramids of Giza (Aug 3-4). Eileen Hotel is near Tahrir Square/Nile Corniche.\",\n          \"category\": \"observation\",\n          \"trip_part\": \"cairo\",\n          \"related_contact\": \"\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"a3f4b401-fa28-4d6b-a5c8-19a2f1d47de9\",\n          \"title\": \"Cairo Stopover 2 sightseeing\",\n          \"body\": \"Islamic Cairo, the Citadel, Khan el-Khalili bazaar, Coptic Cairo (Aug 19-20). Ramses Hilton is the base; taxi needed between Citadel and Coptic Cairo.\",\n          \"category\": \"observation\",\n          \"trip_part\": \"cairo\",\n          \"related_contact\": \"\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"faefd84c-604e-43ba-b315-93b242f005f8\",\n          \"title\": \"Dar es Salaam exploration ideas\",\n          \"body\": \"Arriving by ferry from Zanzibar; interest in city exploration: Kivukoni Fish Market, Kariakoo Market, National Museum, Coco Beach, Bongoyo Island.\",\n          \"category\": \"observation\",\n          \"trip_part\": \"dar\",\n          \"related_contact\": \"\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    \"appManifest\": {\n      \"tables\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"contacts\",\n          \"schema\": {\n            \"title\": \"Contacts & People\",\n            \"description\": \"All contacts, service providers, and people involved in the trip.\",\n            \"columns\": {\n              \"id\": {\n                \"type\": \"string\",\n                \"description\": \"Primary key\",\n                \"primaryKey\": true,\n                \"generated\": \"uuid\"\n              },\n              \"name\": {\n                \"type\": \"string\",\n                \"description\": \"Name of person or business\"\n              },\n              \"role\": {\n                \"type\": \"string\",\n   